description: Retrieves information about the delegated Amazon Macie administrator account for an organization in Organizations.

nested_items.name: adminAccounts
nested_items.description: An array of objects, one for each delegated Amazon Macie administrator account for the organization. Only one of these accounts can have a status of ENABLED.

nested_items.name: accountId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID for the account.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The current status of the account as the delegated Amazon Macie administrator account for the organization.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The string to use in a subsequent request to get the next page of results in a paginated response. This value is null if there are no additional pages.
